## Type of Bug Request

<!-- Delete or cross off bullet points that are irrelevant to this Issue: -->

## Type of Entry Request

<!-- Delete or cross off bullet points that are irrelevant to this Issue: -->

- Recommend change(s) to documentation (such as existing text or new text)
